Swiggg Sales

1)Project Title
The purpose of creating a swiggy sales is to turn large volumes of order and revenue data into a clear, real-time view of business performance so teams can make faster and better decisions.

2) Purpose
A Swiggy sales project is not just about numbers—it’s about learning how to analyze a real business, generate insights, and support smarter decisions using data.

3) Tech Stack
The Project was built using the following tools and technologies:

Jupyter Notebook : Main programming platform used for report creation.
Pandas Library : Main Module which is used to import the data.
seaborn Library : Data Visualization tool used in python.
matplotlib Library :  Data Visualization tool used in python.
plotly Library :  Data Visualization tool used in python.

4) Data Source
This Project is built using sample/synthetic Restaurant data modeled to represent and serve the purpose of delivery like operations.

5) Features and Highlights
5.1) Bussiness Problem
This swiggy sales project/report helps to solve several common business problems like 
👉 Analyse sales performance
👉 Detect customer behavior
👉 Predict operational efficiency
👉 Take data-driven decision

 5.2) Goal Of The Project
The goal of this project is to analyze business data and turn it into actionable insights that improve performance and decision-making.

